023package org.biojava.nbio.structure.align.helper;
024
025public class GapArray {
026
027
028
029                public int index;
030                public int value;
031
032                public GapArray() {
033                        super();
034
035                        index =0;
036                        value=0;
037                }
038
039                public int getIndex() {
040                        return index;
041                }
042                public void setIndex(int index) {
043                        this.index = index;
044                }
045                public int getValue() {
046                        return value;
047                }
048                public void setValue(int value) {
049                        this.value = value;
050                }
051
052
053        }
